import React from "react";
import { Button, Image, List } from 'semantic-ui-react'
function Card(props) {
console.log(props.song)
  return (
    <React.Fragment>
        <List divided verticalAlign='middle'>
    <List.Item>
      <List.Content floated='right'>
        <Button>Add</Button>
      </List.Content>
      <Image avatar src={props.song.artworkUrl100}/>
      <List.Content><audio style={{height:"10px"}} controls>
        <source src={props.song.previewUrl}></source>
        </audio></List.Content>
    </List.Item>
  </List>
    </React.Fragment>
  )
}

export default Card;
